8x768.webp 768w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/delicious-individual-chicken-pot-pie-1-500x500.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" title="High-Protein Cinnamon Roll Bread with Cottage Cheese Recipe for Breakfast 2"></noscript></a><h2 class="gb-text gb-text-d5890229"><a href="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/delicious-individual-chicken-pot-pie/">Delicious Individual Chicken Pot Pie</a></h2><p class="gb-text gb-text-94745f06">December 3, 2025</p></div><div class="gb-loop-item gb-loop-item-b81e556d post-12975 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-pastries no-featured-image-padding">
<a href="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="1024" data-media-id="13346" class="gb-media-8eeb01e4 perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;1024&#039;%20height=&#039;1024&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%201024%201024&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Easy Sour Dough Starter Pizza Dough Recipe" title="High-Protein Cinnamon Roll Bread with Cottage Cheese Recipe for Breakfast 3" data-src="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2.webp" data-srcset="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2.webp 1024w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-300x300.webp 300w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-150x150.webp 150w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-768x768.webp 768w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-500x500.webp 500w" data-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="1024" data-media-id="13346" class="gb-media-8eeb01e4" src="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2.webp" alt="Easy Sour Dough Starter Pizza Dough Recipe" srcset="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2.webp 1024w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-300x300.webp 300w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-150x150.webp 150w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-768x768.webp 768w, https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough-recipe-1-2-500x500.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" title="High-Protein Cinnamon Roll Bread with Cottage Cheese Recipe for Breakfast 3"></noscript></a><h2 class="gb-text gb-text-d5890229"><a href="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/easy-sour-dough-starter-pizza-dough/">Easy Sour Dough Starter Pizza Dough Recipe</a></h2><p class="gb-text gb-text-94745f06">February 14, 2026</p></div></div></div></div><div class="gb-element-11dac3f9"><p class="gb-text gb-text-68264ae0"><a href="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/pastries/" target="_blank" data-type="category" data-id="1" rel="noreferrer noopener">See All Recipes</a>&#8230;</p></div></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading">How To Store <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/health-canada/services/general-food-safety-tips/food-safety-tips-leftovers.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leftovers</a></h2><p>Got any leftover High Protein Cottage Cheese Cinnamon Roll Bread? Lucky you! Store it in an airtight container at room temperature for up to 2 days. If you need it to last longer, pop it in the <a href="https://www.foodauthority.nsw.gov.au/consumer/special-care-foods/leftovers" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">refrigerator</a> for up to a week. It also freezes beautifully, so feel free to slice and freeze portions for future quick breakfasts.</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading">Tips</h2><p>Want to make this recipe even better? Try adding a sprinkle of chopped nuts to the cinnamon swirl for a little crunch. If you don&#8217;t have oat flour, almond flour works great and keeps it gluten-free. And remember, blending the cottage cheese really is the secret to that super moist texture.</p><p>This is a truly versatile recipe. It’s one of those <strong>breakfast ideas</strong> that works perfectly as a quick snack too. You might even find yourself enjoying it as one of your favorite <strong>high protein baked snacks</strong>.</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading">Conclusion</h2><p>So there you have it! A delicious, protein packed, and super easy way to enjoy a cinnamon roll vibe any time of day. This <strong>High Protein Cottage Cheese Cinnamon Roll Bread</strong> is proof that <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/live-well/eat-well/how-to-eat-a-balanced-diet/eight-tips-for-healthy-eating/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><a href="https://www.myplate.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">healthy</a> eating</a> can be incredibly satisfying and fun. It’s a fantastic addition to your list of go-to <strong>breakfast ideas with protein</strong>.</p><p>Give it a try and let us know what you think! It&#8217;s a wonderful example of how you can create amazing <strong>protein breakfast baked goods</strong> right in your own kitchen without a fuss.</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading">FAQ</h2><h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can I use regular flour instead of oat flour?</h3><p>Yes, you can use all purpose flour. The texture might be slightly different, but it will still be delicious. Just use the same amount.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading">Is this recipe good for meal prep?</h3><p>Absolutely! This <strong>protein sweet breakfast</strong> loaf is perfect for meal prep. Bake it on Sunday and have slices ready for busy mornings all week long. It holds up well.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can I make this recipe gluten-free?</h3><p>Yes, you can! Simply substitute the oat flour with almond flour, and ensure your other ingredients are certified gluten-free. It makes for wonderful <strong>protein breads</strong>.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading">What other ways can I use cottage cheese in baking?</h3><p>Cottage cheese is fantastic in baking! It adds moisture and protein. You can use it in pancakes, muffins, and even as a base for creamy desserts, like in these <strong>recipes with cottage cheese desserts</strong>.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading">How much protein is in one serving?</h3><p>This loaf provides over 20 grams of protein per slice, making it a substantial and filling option. It&#8217;s one of the best <strong>high protein breads</strong> you can make.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can I add other flavors to the swirl?</h3><p>Definitely! You could add a pinch of nutmeg or cardamom to the cinnamon swirl for extra warmth. Some chopped pecans or walnuts would also be a yummy addition to this <strong>Yummy Loaf Recipe</strong>.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading">Is the glaze necessary?</h3><p>The glaze is totally optional but adds a nice touch of sweetness and visual appeal. The bread is delicious on its own even without it!</p><script type="application/ld+json">{
