<a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01GHECG68?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="product-card"><div class="image-container-small">
<img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;0&#039;%20height=&#039;0&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%200%200&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Light Brown Sugar" title="High-Protein Cinnamon Roll Bread with Cottage Cheese Recipe for Breakfast 9" class="perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41tUYzSpLpL._SL160_.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41tUYzSpLpL._SL160_.jpg" alt="Light Brown Sugar" title="High-Protein Cinnamon Roll Bread with Cottage Cheese Recipe for Breakfast 9"></noscript></div><div class="product-title-small">
Light Brown Sugar</div>
</a></div></div><h3 class="section-title">Ingredients</h3><div class="ingredients-list"><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing1"><label for="ing1">1¼ cups cottage cheese (blended until smooth)</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing2"><label for="ing2">1 large egg</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing3"><label for="ing3">2 tbsp maple syrup or honey</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing4"><label for="ing4">1 tsp <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0046EJ570?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">vanilla extract</a></label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing5"><label for="ing5">2 cups oat flour (or <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06XCGLRNL?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">almond flour</a> for gluten-free)</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing6"><label for="ing6">1 tsp baking powder</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing7"><label for="ing7">¼ tsp baking soda</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing8"><label for="ing8">Pinch of salt</label></div><h4 style="margin: 15px 0 5px; color: var(--primary);">For the Cinnamon Swirl</h4><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing9"><label for="ing9">⅓ cup coconut sugar or <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01GHECG68?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">brown sugar</a></label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing10"><label for="ing10">2 tbsp melted <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07VF6RXNL?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">butter</a> or coconut oil</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing11"><label for="ing11">1½ tsp <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07W1WVMDM?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">cinnamon</a></label></div><h4 style="margin: 15px 0 5px; color: var(--primary);">Optional Glaze</h4><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing12"><label for="ing12">½ cup <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07NRZTSH1?tag=cookfastrecip-20&#038;linkCode=osi&#038;th=1&#038;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">powdered sugar</a></label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing13"><label for="ing13">1–2 tbsp blended cottage cheese or Greek yogurt</label></div><div class="ingredient-item"><input type="checkbox" id="ing14"><label for="ing14">Splash of vanilla or milk to thin</label></div></div><h3 class="section-title">Instructions</h3><ol class="instructions-list"><li class="instruction-step">Preheat your oven to 350°F. Grease a loaf pan and line it with <a href="https://amzn.to/3LaaUUl" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">parchment paper</a> for easy removal later.</li><li class="instruction-step">Place the cottage cheese into a <a href="https://amzn.to/4ofMjff" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">blender</a> or food processor. Blend until it is completely smooth with no lumps.</li><li class="instruction-step">In a large bowl, whisk together the smooth cottage cheese, egg, maple syrup (or honey), and vanilla extract until well combined.</li><li class="instruction-step">In a separate bowl, whisk together the oat flour, baking powder, baking soda, and a pinch of salt.</li><li class="instruction-step">Stir the dry ingredients into the wet mixture until a thick batter forms. Do not overmix.</li><li class="instruction-step">In a small bowl, make the swirl by mixing the sugar, melted butter, and cinnamon into a spreadable paste.</li><li class="instruction-step">Pour half of the batter into the prepared loaf pan. Spoon half of the cinnamon mixture over the top and swirl gently with a knife.</li><li class="instruction-step">Add the remaining batter, followed by the rest of the cinnamon mixture. Swirl again to create marble patterns.</li><li class="instruction-step">Bake for 30 to 35 minutes, or until a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean. Let the loaf cool in the pan.</li><li class="instruction-step">Optional: Whisk powdered sugar, cottage cheese/yogurt, and milk to make a glaze. Drizzle over the cooled bread.</li></ol><h3 class="section-title">Notes</h3><div class="notes-section"><p>Blending the cottage cheese is the secret to the smooth, moist texture. Don&#8217;t skip this step!</p><p>Leftovers can be stored in an airtight container at room temperature for 2 days or in the refrigerator for up to a week.</p><p>This bread freezes beautifully. Slice it up and freeze individual portions for a super quick breakfast later.</p><p>For extra crunch, try adding chopped nuts like pecans or walnuts to the cinnamon swirl mixture.</p></div><div class="nutrition-section"><h3>Nutrition</h3><div class="nutrition-grid"><div class="nutrition-item"><strong>240</strong><br>Calories</div><div class="nutrition-item"><strong>9g</strong><br>Sugar</div><div class="nutrition-item"><strong>6g</strong><br>Fat</div><div class="nutrition-item"><strong>26g</strong><br>Carbs</div><div class="nutrition-item"><strong>20g</strong><br>Protein</div></div></div></div> <script src="data:text/javascript;base64," defer type="pmdelayedscript" data-cfasync="false" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1" data-no-minify="1"></script> </p></div></div><div class="gb-element-8d0249bd"><div class="gb-element-a75aec6e"><div class="gb-element-4dc05180"><h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">About the Author</h3><div class="gb-element-1dca7bca">
<img width="100" height="100" decoding="async" class="gb-media-88d8f3cc perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;100&#039;%20height=&#039;100&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20100%20100&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/cropped-Merek-Halvar-100x100.webp" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" decoding="async" class="gb-media-88d8f3cc" src="https://www.cookfastrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/cropped-Merek-Halvar-100x100.webp"/></noscript><div><div class="gb-text gb-text-51810f65">James Carter</div><div class="gb-text gb-text-0900d79e">February 24, 2026</div></div></div><div class="gb-text gb-text-7f20e71e">I learned to cook from two amazing women: my mom and my aunt. My mom, who passed away in 2021, was the heart of our kitchen. I've stayed in the home we shared, continuing the tradition of home-cooked meals that bring comfort and connection.</div></div></div></div><div class="gb-element-bb8a9aca"><div class="gb-element-9e4aa40a"><h2 class="gb-text gb-text-253ac52f">Recipes You'll Love</h2></div><div class="gb-query-50178d5f"><div class="gb-looper-f9e3d458"><div class="gb-loop-item gb-loop-item-fdfb89db post-8814 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-snacks no-featured-image-padding">
